\[
countfunc(limitvar) \sim \int_0^{\sqrt{limitvar}} 2 \sqrt{dummyvar} \,d dummyvar = \frac{4}{3} limitvar^{3/4}.
\]
To make this precise, we use the bounds $dummyvar-1 \leq \lfloor dummyvar \rfloor \leq dummyvar$,
