\frac{4}{3} (limitvar-1)^{3/4} + \frac{2}{3} (limitvar-1)^{1/4}
&\leq
countfunc(\lfloor limitvar^{1/4} \rfloor^4) \\
&\leq countfunc(limitvar) \\
&\leq countfunc(\lceil limitvar^{1/4} \rceil^4) \\
&\leq \frac{4}{3} (limitvar+1)^{3/4} + \frac{2}{3} (limitvar+1)^{1/4}
\end{align*}
to obtain the desired limit.

